commitResults.messageTitle: Added Basic structure of IOManager, can only echo input except "bye".
Added support for addition and listing
commitResults.messageBody: Added support for more functionalities. The matching of operation type is currently handled by the InputType enum, while the action is handled by the InputHandler. TODO : combine the action handler in with the enum itself.
The enums now handle both checking as well as doing the action they are associated with in the form of lambdas. InputHandler just passes in those functions to the enums.

commitResults.messageTitle: Exception Handling for Done, TODO, and UNKNOWN added.
Deletion support added. Bug fixed regarding task done.

commitResults.messageBody:
Previously everything was stored in the temporary memory.
Created an interface for saveing the task list, and made an implementation where everything is stored in a local file.

commitResults.messageTitle: Add support for LocalDate in Deadline
commitResults.messageBody:
Previously, entered date was not interpreted as a date.

Now added support and made it an actual LocalDate object.

Earlier all the code was in the core package.
Created another package that specifically contain task related classes and interfaces.

Added some simple testing for a few public methods in TaskManager, and TodoTask creation.

Also updated TaskManager to have a boolean parameter based on which it will load from storage or start a new file altogether.
Added documentation to the public methods. Updated gitignore to ignore the manifest files from JAR creation.

Added support for keyword finding, and fixed bug w.r.t loading fails
when storage file throws ClassCastException.

commitResults.messageTitle: Change method name to match Coding Standard
commitResults.messageBody: Change the name of getDone to setDone in Task.java
